"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17692,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/22\/abu-bakr-becomes-al-siddiq\/","url_meta":{"origin":6719,"position":3},"title":"Abu Bakr on Truth: How Abu Bakr got the name al-Siddiq","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 22, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: After the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was miraculously taken by night to the furthest mosque in Jerusalem, the people began to talk about it. Some of them renounced their faith and belief in him. They sought Abu Bakr and they said, \u201cHave you heard that\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11077,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/06\/after-prophet-khulafah-rashidun\/","url_meta":{"origin":6719,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: After the Prophet, follow Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: We were sitting with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cI surely do not know how much longer I will remain with you. After me, follow these two,\u201d and the Prophet pointed to Abu Bakr and Umar. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3663 Grade:\u00a0Hasan (fair)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","sr